<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">These are Adult Comics. Graphically and conceptually. I see a lot of people talking about excessive sex and profanity but the same people don&apos;t make t<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">These are Adult Comics. Graphically and conceptually. I see a lot of people talking about excessive sex and profanity but the same people don't make the same remarks about the physical violence. Not that I'm especially shocked about it but considering the percentage of both I'd say violence wins.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
