<div id="review_2089939572" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2089939572" />
    <a title="Zoë" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9303625-zo"><img alt="Zoë" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1580008879p2/9303625.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2089939572?book_show_action=true">Aug 11, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Zoë" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Zoë" href="/user/show/9303625-zo">Zoë</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2089939572" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11030055666555523027">This universe looks so <i>cool</i>. I can&apos;t stop staring at the characters and the vivid worlds. It&apos;s gorgeous. <br/>However, the plot itself isn&apos;t as unique or fleshed out, and there are quite a few upsetting moments. For example, the unnecessary use of the &quot;r&quot; word. <a class='jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction'>(view spoiler)</a><span class='spoilerContainer' style='display: none'>[Also, using a six-year-old child forced into prostitution as a device to show that our bounty hunter is really a &quot;good guy&quot;? Why??? <a class='jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction'>(hide spoiler)</a>]</span><br/>It is often vulgar with explicit sex scenes, strong language, gore, and violence.</span>
  <span id="freeText11030055666555523027" style="display:none">This universe looks so <i>cool</i>. I can't stop staring at the characters and the vivid worlds. It's gorgeous. <br />However, the plot itself isn't as unique or fleshed out, and there are quite a few upsetting moments. For example, the unnecessary use of the "r" word. <a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Also, using a six-year-old child forced into prostitution as a device to show that our bounty hunter is really a "good guy"? Why??? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span><br />It is often vulgar with explicit sex scenes, strong language, gore, and violence. So make sure to keep that in mind if you read in public!<br />I see potential in this story to improve and have been recommended these books again and again, so I'm going to continue on.</span>
