<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer6786802168043859893">Brian K. Vaughan is the writer and co-creator of comic-book series including SAGA, PAPER GIRLS, Y THE LAST MAN, RUNAWAYS, and most recently, BARRIER, a digital comic with artist Marcos Martin about immigration, available from their pay-what-you-want site <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://www.PanelSyndicate.com'>www.PanelSyndicate.com</a><br/><br/>BKV&apos;s work has been recognized at the Eisner, Harvey, Hugo, Shuster, Eagle, and British Fantasy Awards. He sometimes writes</span>
  <span id="freeText6786802168043859893" style="display:none">Brian K. Vaughan is the writer and co-creator of comic-book series including SAGA, PAPER GIRLS, Y THE LAST MAN, RUNAWAYS, and most recently, BARRIER, a digital comic with artist Marcos Martin about immigration, available from their pay-what-you-want site <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.PanelSyndicate.com">www.PanelSyndicate.com</a><br /><br />BKV's work has been recognized at the Eisner, Harvey, Hugo, Shuster, Eagle, and British Fantasy Awards. He sometimes writes for film and television in Los Angeles, where he lives with his family and their dogs Hamburger and Milkshake. </span>
